Installation:
    READONLY access:
        git clone git://github.com/gordyt/vim.git ~/.vim

    READ/WRITE access:
        git clone git@github.com:gordyt/vim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule update --init


Then switch to the '~/.vim/bundle/pyflake-vim' directory and fetch
the pyflake submodule:

    cd ~/.vim/bundle/pyflake-vim
    git submodule update --init

NOTES: 

If you want to use the pep8 submodule then you need to install pep8:

sudo easy_intall pep8

If you want to use the javasScriptLint.vim submodule then you need to intall jsl:

via homebrew: brew install jsl
